shortDescription: Deconovo decorative velvet pillow covers can update your living room or family room in a simple, stylish and inexpensive way. These decorative pillowcases add a touch of contemporary style and comfort to your indoor and outdoor furnishings. These short plush, eye-catching cushion covers with multiple colors and sizes add a splash of vibrant color to your sofa, couch, chair, bench, or patio chair, and the practically hidden zipper on the side makes it easy to insert and remove sham or insert. For a fluffy look, always use the larger size insert. Size: 2 pack 16x16 inch/40x40 cm pink pillow covers(please allow 1-2cm measurement deviation). No pillow insert or filler. Material: Our throw pillow covers are made of 100% velvet fabric, super soft and delicate, with a light luster. Also pet and child friendly.
